        {
            "title": "A股午後下滑 滬股失4000關  一周計滬深累跌約3%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股午後顯著向下，滬股失4000關，深股失守14000，兩市成交合計22868.1億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-17.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-17.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬綜指全日報3957點，跌49點或1.24%，早段高見4022，升16點或0.4%，即反覆向下，午後破上午低位，見3955點，跌51點或1.27%，全日成交9648.63億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">全周跌138點或3.37%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深成指全日報13866，跌35點或0.25%，早段區間上落，午後初段見14144，升143點或1.03%，為全日高位，隨即迅速向下，再失14000關，臨近收市見後13856，跌45點或0.32%，低見13954，為全日低位，全日成交13219.48億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">全周累跌414點或或2.9%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300全日報4567，跌16點或0.35%，創業板全日報3352，升43點或1.3%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15767093-a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e4%b8%8b%e6%bb%91-%e6%bb%ac%e8%82%a1%e5%a4%b14000%e9%97%9c-%e4%b8%80%e5%91%a8%e8%a8%88%e6%bb%ac%e6%b7%b1%e7%b4%af%e8%b7%8c%e7%b4%843",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-8.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-20 15:30:53",
