            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">大唐西市絲路投資控股(00620)將於今天（20/3/2026）下午一時正起短暫停止買賣。</p>\n</div>",
